data.description: So much space! A great house in the North Star subdivision with an abundance of space for everyone. The open and inviting main level seamlessly connects a spacious kitchen, a warm and welcoming great room, and a cozy gas fireplace. The primary bedroom and two additional bedrooms are conveniently located on the main floor. Downstairs you will find a sprawling basement with space to host game day football parties, for the kids to have indoor play space, or for you to enjoy your hobbies. Need more room for guests? The lower level has two extra-large bedrooms and a bathroom providing a private Montana retreat. The backyard is fenced, and the three-car garage provides tons of space for your outdoor toys. The roof is brand new. This house is waiting for your personal touches to make it your home. Schedule a showing today.
